OL,5, Falling food costs helped shop price   
OL,6, inflation ease to its lowest level in  
OL,7, more than two years, figures show.     
OL,9,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC),   
OL,10,Fwhich represents supermarkets, said the
OL,11,Frate at which prices were rising had   
OL,12,Falmost halved to 1.3% in March - down  
OL,13,Ffrom 2.5% in February.                 
OL,15,FBut it said Easter treats remained more
OL,16,Fexpensive than in previous years       
OL,17,Fbecause of high cocoa and sugar prices.
OL,19,FIt is the tenth month in a row food    
OL,20,Fprice inflation has fallen.            
